org.pebble.types

Class TypeMapDecoder<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.pebble.types.TypeIntDecoder<T>
      • org.pebble.types.TypeMapDecoder<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - type supported by the encoder.
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    TextIntDecoder, UUIDIntDecoder

    public abstract class TypeMapDecoder<T>
extends TypeIntDecoder<T>
    Abstract class used to recover list of original complex types from an encoded list of integers obtained using an extending instance of TypeMapEncoder. This class takes the list index stored on the integer list to lookup the offset of the encoded original complex type and decodes the stored value.
